<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>白骨精坐在路边，又在空气里闻了闻。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25839</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“唐僧有些很厉害的同伴。”她说，“我得伪装一下。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25840</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36175</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒扔下了行李。“我累了，也饿了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36176</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39623</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们停下吃午饭吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39624</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空用他的千里眼看到了千里之外的一片桃林。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47581</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一会儿就回来。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50904</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空离开了没一会儿，一个年轻的女人向他们走了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64614</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把一只碗递了过来。“您是唐僧吗？”她问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64615</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71529</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有食物给您。”八戒拿过了那个碗：“谢谢你！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71530</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76838</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别吃！”悟空飞快地飞了回来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76839</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把桃子扔在了地上，拿出了金箍棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81924</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嘣！他朝着那个年轻女子打过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86324</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91040</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他还没打到那个女子，她就不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91041</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96287</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你为什么要这么做？”唐僧大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99577</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是人，师父。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99578</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你看不出来那个女的其实是个妖精，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107832</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她想要伤害你。可惜，让她逃走了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107833</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你为什么这么残忍？”唐僧问，“她正要给我们食物。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121525</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那不是食物。”悟空说，“看到了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121526</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他举起了那个碗，里面都是虫子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126554</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别相信悟空。”八戒说，“他用法术把食物变成了虫子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134398</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140243</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒看着那个女子原来站着的地方，摇摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140244</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空打得太重了，她什么都没有了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这简直太可笑了！”悟空说，“我......啊啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152991</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧念起了紧箍咒，悟空在地上滚来滚去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164894</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒大笑：“我不知道你会这个啊，师父。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164895</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170710</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这个时候，一个老婆婆向他们走了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170711</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧停止了念咒，悟空站了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181989</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在找我的女儿。”老婆婆说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181990</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189694</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她给唐僧拿吃的来了。” “哎呀！”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189695</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196731</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒跨步向前：“你应该问那只猴子你的女儿出了什么事。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196732</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空近距离地看了那个老婆婆一会儿，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202924</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209910</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后他拿出了金箍棒打过去，但他又打偏了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209911</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214078</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她又跑了！”悟空大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214079</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221638</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他又杀了一个无辜的人！”八戒大叫，“师父，快念咒！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221639</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧又开始念紧箍咒。悟空痛苦地倒在了地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229729</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请停下吧！”悟空大叫。唐僧停止了念咒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要再伤害任何人了。”他说，“如果你再伤人，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我就念咒念到你脑袋爆炸。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245192</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249576</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，路上又来了一个老大爷。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249577</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254266</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在找我的妻子和女儿。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254267</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“又是那个女妖精。”悟空想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260997</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264758</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果我不打死她，她就会伤害唐僧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264759</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270290</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但如果我伤了她，唐僧就会让我的脑袋爆炸。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270291</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空叹了口气。“我必须保护唐僧，不管发生什么事情。”他想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空拿出了金箍棒打了过去。一阵烟雾飘过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285171</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290796</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当烟雾散去的时候，地上躺了一具白骨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290797</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297444</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我打中她了！”悟空大叫，“看到了吗？她就是个白骨精！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297445</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304962</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧皱眉。“再念咒吧！”八戒对唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304963</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309706</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望你离开，悟空。”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309707</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“师父。”悟空说，“我刚刚救了你的命呀。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315924</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不相信你。”唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>323792</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你现在就走，要不我就要念紧箍咒了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>323793</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>330310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空生气了：“如果你真的想要我走，我就走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>330311</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>335651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，以后你需要帮助的时候，别想我会回来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>335652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>343855</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跳到空中消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>